-- Pertamina Said to Buy Akpo, Es Sharara Crude From Cnooc
-- B y   C h r i s t i a n   S c h m o l l i n g e r   a n d   S h e r r y   S u
-- 2012-07-26T10:51:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-26/pertamina-said-to-buy-akpo-es-sharara-crude-from-cnooc-1-.html
PT Pertamina,  Indonesia ’s state-
owned oil company, bought 950,000 barrels each of Nigerian Akpo
and Libyan Es Sharara crude from  Cnooc Ltd. (883)  via a tender,
according to four people who participate in the market.  The crude will be delivered in October to Pertamina’s
refinery at Balikpapan, the people said, declining to be
identified because the information is confidential.  To contact the reporters on this story:
